snippet.title: Something Like A Party [Keira Knightley | Amber Heard | Emma Watson]
snippet.description:
Nothing like a good old fashioned sense of girl power.

Prompt: Music Video

This is definitely not a pairing. This video is just something that I thought of when I recieved that prompt. Keira, Amber, and Emma creating a band together. Crazy right?

I am now taking requests! Send me prompts, couple pairings, or a song that you would like me to do and I will add it to the list of my requests!
